---
import Head from "../../components/Head.astro";
import Header from "../../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../../components/Footer.astro";
import { Buttons } from "../../components/Buttons";

const buttons = [{ id: 204, size: "XL" }];
---

<html>
  <Head
    title="Tire Calligraphy - Hybrid Jacket"
    url="https://tirecalli.com/hybrid-jacket/"
    description="A hybrid item. A versatile servant of your expectations and needs when fighting the elements. Consists of two pieces; this being TC Basic Denim Jacket and the second one, TC Black Quilted Jacket. A neutral-gender item."
  />
  <body>
    <Header />
    <main>
      <article class="product">
        <aside class="product__aside">
          <div class="product__figures">
            <a href="details.html#photo-1"
              ><img src="/img/Hybrid-Jacket/girl-in-hybrid-winter-jacket.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" />
              <div class="product__exclusive bold"><p>WEB EXCLUSIVE</p></div>
            </a>
            <a href="details.html#photo-2"
              ><img src="/img/Hybrid-Jacket/hybrid-winter-jacket-back-detail.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" />
              <div class="product__exclusive bold text--white"><p>WEB EXCLUSIVE</p></div>
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="product__figures">
            <a href="details.html#photo-3"
              ><img src="/img/Hybrid-Jacket/girl-in-hybrid-winter-jacket-front-detail.webp" loading="lazy" alt="tirecalli-picture" />
            </a>
            <a href="details.html#photo-4"><img src="/img/Hybrid-Jacket/hybrid-winter-jacket-back-detail-2.webp" loading="lazy" alt="tirecalli-picture" /></a>
          </div>
          <div class="product__figures">
            <a href="details.html#photo-5"><img src="/img/Hybrid-Jacket/man-in-hybrid-winter-jacket-front.webp" loading="lazy" alt="tirecalli-picture" /></a>
            <a href="details.html#photo-6"
              ><img src="/img/Hybrid-Jacket/man-in-hybrid-winter-jacket-front-detail.webp" loading="lazy" alt="tirecalli-picture" />
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="product__figures">
            <a href="details.html#photo-7"
              ><img src="/img/Hybrid-Jacket/man-in-hybrid-winter-jacket-botton-up.webp" loading="lazy" alt="tirecalli-picture" />
            </a>
            <a href="details.html#photo-8"><img src="/img/Hybrid-Jacket/man-in-hybrid-winter-jacket-close-up.webp" loading="lazy" alt="tirecalli-picture" /></a>
          </div>
          <div class="product__figures">
            <a href="details.html#photo-9"><img src="/img/Hybrid-Jacket/girl-in-hybrid-jacket-3.webp" loading="lazy" alt="tirecalli-picture" /></a>
            <a href="details.html#photo-10"><img src="/img/Hybrid-Jacket/man-in-hybrid-jacket-4.webp" loading="lazy" alt="tirecalli-picture" /></a>
          </div>
        </aside>
        <section class="product__info">
          <div class="product__item">
            <h2>HYBRID JACKET</h2>
            <h2>199144</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--price">
            <p>Price: 250€</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--size-select">
            <p>Select your size and add to bag</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--sizes">
            <Buttons client:load items={buttons} />
          </div>

          <div class="product__item product__item--description">
            <p>
              A hybrid item. A versatile servant of your expectations and needs when fighting the elements. Consists of two pieces; this being TC Basic Denim
              Jacket, which can be worn as a single item, enriching your style through warmer months of early Spring and Fall, and the second one, TC Black
              Quilted Jacket. The denim layer is crafted from raw black denim, fitted oversized with 90s hip hop scene as an inspo, whilst honoring the
              aesthetics of the 21st century Far East, this again being Korea and Japan. The quilted layer is created true to size. This item can be worn as a
              standalone protector from cold or can be styled two ways with the TC Basic Denim Jacket. Primarily envisioned as an inner layer, this one will
              serve your style as an outer layer as well.
            </p>
            <p>Ofc, this item is neutral gender, crafted according to TC vision of universal wearability.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--accordion">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div>
                <input type="checkbox" name="panel" id="panel-1" />
                <label for="panel-1">Details</label>
                <div class="accordion__content accordion__content--panel-1">
                  <ul class="accordion__list accordion-panel-1__list">
                    <li>A gender-neutral cut</li>
                    <li>6 pocket design: 2 chest pockets, 2 side + 2 inner pockets</li>
                    <li>Removable, inner layer</li>
                    <li>Color: Black</li>
                    <li>Material: 100% raw denim cotton (550 g, 19.4oz)</li>
                    <li>Care: Machine-wash cold, warm (30°C)</li>
                    <li>Proudly created in Croatia from local craftswomen and men</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--accordion">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div>
                <input type="checkbox" name="panel" id="panel-2" />
                <label for="panel-2">Size & Fit</label>
                <div class="accordion__content accordion__content--panel-2">
                  <ul class="accordion__list accordion-panel-2__list">
                    <li>Karla is wearing size S and is 165cm/5.4 ft tall</li>
                    <li>Boban is wearing L and is 187cm /6.13 ft tall</li>
                    <li>Loose, oversized fit, you can size up or size down</li>
                  </ul>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="product__item product__item--accordion">
            <div class="accordion">
              <div>
                <input type="checkbox" name="panel" id="panel-3" />
                <label for="panel-3">Shipping & Returns</label>
                <div class="accordion__content accordion__content--panel-3">
                  <div class="accordion__copy">
                    <p class="accordion__body">Standard shipping and 30-day returns.</p>
                    <p class="accordion__body">Return policy exclusions apply.</p>
                    <p class="accordion__body">
                      <a href="/legal">Learn more.</a>
                    </p>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
      </article>
      <section class="upsell">
        <h2>You might also like</h2>
        <div class="upsell__group">
          <a href="/Basic-Denim-Overall-Pant/">
            <div class="upsell__item">
              <img src="/img/Basic-Denim-Overall-Pant/girl-in-basic-denim-overall-pant-2.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" />
              <h5>Basic Denim Overall Pant</h5>
            </div>
          </a>
          <a href="/Sand-Brown-Licitar-T-Shirt/">
            <div class="upsell__item">
              <img src="/img/Sand-Brown-Licitar-T-Shirt/girl-in-sand-brown-licitar-t-shirt-back.webp" alt="tirecalli-picture" loading="lazy" />
              <h5>Sand Brown Licitar T-Shirt</h5>
            </div>
          </a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <Footer />
    <script src="../../js/app.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
